Scouting report: TONS of buck sign in a very untouched spot (especially for #puremichigan during r!fle szn), a few deer, and the mother load of chaga (if you don’t know what it is, look it up and then go find some 👌). All made possible by the @unchartedsupplyco inflatable raft. Game changer for us - we love hunting swampy islands. 

We’ll be back to this spot!
